prompt:
List some common complaints that users might have about a website or web application that you have used recently.
Recently, I have been using a popular web platform for social networking purposes. The site has several features that I enjoy, but there are also some issues that I encounter on a regular basis. These complaints include:
• The website often takes too long to load, causing frustration and wasting time.
• Some features of the site can be confusing to use, leading to user errors and wasted effort.
• The design of certain parts of the site is unappealing, making it less enjoyable to use.
